import React, {
  Fragment,
  Component
} from 'react';
import {
  Helmet
} from 'react-helmet';
/* import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; */
/* import { Button } from 'materialize-css'; */

class Register extends Component {
  render() {
    return ( <
      Fragment >
      <
      Helmet > < title > Nimelssa Quiz - Registeation page < /title></Helmet >
      <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      form className = "col s12"
      autoComplete = "off" >
      <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "col s12 m4 offset-m4" >
      <
      div className = "card z-depth-4" >
      <
      div className = "card-content black white-text" >
      <
      span className = "card-title" > Register < /span> <
      /div> <
      div className = "card-content  white dark-3" >
      <
      div className = "row wrap-input100 validate-input" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > account_circle < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Full Name"
      id = "uid"
      type = "text"
      className = "input100 validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "uid" > User Name < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > edit < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Matric"
      id = "uid"
      type = "number"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "uid" > Matric NUmber < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Password"
      id = "pass"
      type = "password"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "pass"
      className = "active" > Password < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
      input id = "pass"
      type = "password"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required"
      placeholder = "Confirm Password" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "pass"
      className = "active" > Confirm Password < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div >
      <
      label >
      &
      nbsp; < button className = "waves-effect waves-light btn purple"
      style = {
        {
          width: "100%"
        }
      } > Sign Up < /button> <
      /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /form> <
      /div>  <
      /Fragment>
    )
  }
}
export default Register;
